  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to examine connections between muscle tones, strength and
      function after stroke.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Measurements are intended to repeat every two days in acute phase to discover possible
      changes in tone and strength in arm and leg muscles.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
